categories: Category:LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles voice actors

nodes.text: Paulina Gillis (born October 30, 1964) is a Canadian voice actress, comedian and singer who worked primarily for DiC Entertainment and Nelvana, she portrayed Asha in Ewoks and Bene in LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles. She now goes by the name Tabitha St. Germain.
